Stephen D. LEONARD, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2031 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 18, 2017 SUAREZ, LAGOA and FERNANDEZ, JJ., concur.

Petitioner's motion is a duplicate of a motion to produce records in case no. 3D16-2298, which is pending before this Court; therefore, this petition is dismissed as duplicative of the pending appeal.
